flowchart TD
    A["Enter dispatcher<br/>Inputs: request buffer, response buffer"] --> B["Read sub-function byte from request"]
    B --> C{"Sub-function parity?"}

    C -->|Odd = RequestSeed| D{"Special RequestSeed variant?<br/>(sub-function 0x7F)"}
    D -->|Yes| E["Call alternative handler<br/>on response buffer"]
    E --> F["Tag response as alt-handler result"]
    D -->|No| G["Call seed-to-key core<br/>Pass session byte from request"]
    G --> H["Tag response as seed-to-key result"]

    C -->|Even = SendKey| I{"Special SendKey variant?<br/>(sub-function 0x80)"}
    I -->|Yes| J["Call alternative handler<br/>on request buffer"]
    J --> K["Tag response as alt-handler result"]
    I -->|No| L["Call seed-to-key core<br/>Key verification path"]
    L --> K

    F --> M["Write response tag byte"]
    H --> M
    K --> M
    M --> N{"Operation successful?"}
    N -->|Yes| O["Echo sub-function in response<br/>Return success"]
    N -->|No| P["Return negative response code"]
    O --> Q["Run anti-tamper integrity check"]
    P --> Q
    Q --> R["Return to UDS layer"]
